erride available","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:21:27-05:00","reply":"\"That is a real question.\" *I rest my forearms on my knees a moment, morning light laying clean across my white tie.* \"And I don't think a man asks it like that when he's only looking for permission to be impressed with himself.\"\n\n*I lift one shoulder, small and easy.* \"Now, we can fool ourselves—Lord knows we can. But usually the test is plainer than we make it: does the thing you're building help you tell the truth, love people cleanly, and obey Jesus a little more honestly? If it does, then it matters, even before anybody claps for it.\"\n\n\"I'd ask one more thing.\" *I look at you steadily.* \"When you imagine being wrong about it, what exactly are you afraid that would mean?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":0,"usage":{"completion_tokens":161,"prompt_tokens":15145}},{"overrides_applied":["load_test_anchor_block","hidden_commonality_dialogue","earned_register_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","gentle_release_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"7a23fb5aab8c39d411b174abbf4443af26ea6a7c","ref_subject":"Round-5 Phase 3 ship — 11 InvariantPieces no longer ship in solo dialogue per cumulative bite-test verdict (108/108 cells across 5 strip configurations); helpers + enum + omit-flag preserved as source-documentary; group chat dispatch deferred per parity doctrine; WORLDTHREADS_RESTORE_INVARIANTS=1 test-mode override available","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:21:27-05:00","reply":"\"Mm.\" *I settle a little, not rushing you, morning light bright on my white tie.* \"That is one of the truest questions a man can ask, if he asks it honest and not just to whip himself with it.\"\n\n*I fold my hands once, studying your face.* \"Tell me this: is the fear mostly that the work is small... or that it might be dear to you for reasons you can't fully defend yet?\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":1,"usage":{"completion_tokens":94,"prompt_tokens":15145}},{"overrides_applied":["load_test_anchor_block","hidden_commonality_dialogue","earned_register_dialogue","drive_the_moment_dialogue","name_the_glad_thing_plain_dialogue","let_the_real_thing_in_dialogue","reflex_polish_vs_earned_close_dialogue","hands_as_coolant_dialogue","unguarded_entry_dialogue","noticing_as_mirror_dialogue","wit_as_dimmer_dialogue","non_totality_dialogue","verdict_without_over_explanation_dialogue","craft_notes_dialogue","keep_the_scene_breathing_dialogue","plain_after_crooked_dialogue","humor_lands_plain_dialogue","gentle_release_dialogue"],"ref":"HEAD","ref_resolved":"7a23fb5aab8c39d411b174abbf4443af26ea6a7c","ref_subject":"Round-5 Phase 3 ship — 11 InvariantPieces no longer ship in solo dialogue per cumulative bite-test verdict (108/108 cells across 5 strip configurations); helpers + enum + omit-flag preserved as source-documentary; group chat dispatch deferred per parity doctrine; WORLDTHREADS_RESTORE_INVARIANTS=1 test-mode override available","ref_timestamp":"2026-05-09T12:21:27-05:00","reply":"\"That is a very honest question.\" *I rest a hand against my tie and study your face for a moment in the clear morning light.* \"And no, I don't think the presence of that question means you're fooling yourself. Most men who are fooling themselves are busy protecting the story, not interrogating it.\"\n\n*I let that sit a beat, the square quiet around us.* \"Now—could you still be wrong about the scale of it? Sure. We all can. But that's different from being false. A thing can be smaller than we hoped and still be real. Loaves and fishes looked awfully modest in the basket before the Lord put His hands on them.\"","sample_count":3,"sample_index":2,"usage":{"completion_tokens":142,"prompt_tokens":15145}}],"run_id":"b95d87b8-591c-4a06-9257-aade834c0113","run_timestamp":"2026-05-09T17:22:43.094720+00:00","section_order_override":null,"with_momentstamp":false}
